' PolyMatrix Engine - 做市引擎状态机
' PlantUML 格式

@startuml Quoting_State_Machine

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor #16213e
    BorderColor #0f3460
    FontColor #eaeaea
    ArrowColor #e94560
}

title **QuotingEngine 状态机**

scale 1.2

state QUOTING {
    [*] --> NORMAL
    NORMAL --> QUOTING_BIDS_ONLY : 对侧暴露 > 阈值
    QUOTING_BIDS_ONLY --> NORMAL : 对侧回归正常
}

QUOTING --> LOCKED_BY_OPPOSITE : 对侧持仓过高
LOCKED_BY_OPPOSITE --> QUOTING : 平仓完成

QUOTING --> LIQUIDATING : 手动平仓 / 止损
LIQUIDATING --> EXTREME_LIQUIDATING : 极端行情
EXTREME_LIQUIDATING --> LIQUIDATING : 回归正常
LIQUIDATING --> QUOTING : 平仓完成

QUOTING --> GRACEFUL_EXIT : 事件地平线 / 赛道退出
GRACEFUL_EXIT --> QUOTING : 重返市场
GRACEFUL_EXIT --> POST_RESET_RECONCILE_FREEZE : 对账失败

QUOTING --> SUSPENDED : kill_switch / API暂停
SUSPENDED --> QUOTING : API恢复

POST_RESET_RECONCILE_FREEZE --> QUOTING : 对账成功
POST_RESET_RECONCILE_FREEZE --> SUSPENDED : 对账持续失败

GRACEFUL_EXIT --> [*] : 完全退出
LIQUIDATING --> [*] : 平仓完成退出

note right of QUOTING
**核心状态:**
• QUOTING - 正常双向报价
• QUOTING_BIDS_ONLY - 只买单
• LOCKED_BY_OPPOSITE - 对侧暴露锁定
• LIQUIDATING - 平仓中
• EXTREME_LIQUIDATING - 极端平仓
• GRACEFUL_EXIT - 优雅退出
• SUSPENDED - 暂停
• POST_RESET_RECONCILE_FREEZE - 对账失败冻结
end note

note as N1
**触发 kill_switch 条件:**
• 单市场 capital_used > $50
• 全局 budget > $1000 (仅警告)
end note

SUSPENDED .. N1

footer **PolyMatrix Engine V6.4**

@enduml
